## 内容声明

本 Skill 所有训练内容蒸馏自公开出版的运动科学书籍和同行评审论文（见 README 知识库表格与 references/ 内的 `Sources:` 引用）。蒸馏内容属于转述和结构化整理，不复制原书文本。使用者对其训练执行和伤病管理负全部责任。

This Skill's training content is distilled from publicly published sports science books and peer-reviewed papers (see README knowledge table and `Sources:` citations in references/). Distilled content represents paraphrased and structured summaries, not verbatim copies. Users bear full responsibility for training execution and injury management.
